msg: o Httpclient uses commons-logging, which finds log4j in the classpath. Add a configuration file for log4j to stop it from complaining.

author: mrglavas
msg: Improving the performance of toGregorianCalendar(). If the year < 10^9 avoid calling getEonAndYear().
This prevents a new BigInteger from being created.
